data.description:
ASSUMABLE WITH QUALIFYING 2.9% VA LOAN TO QUALIFIED VETERANS -  $91K DOWN -- BALANCE $409K

Breathtaking two-story home on a corner lot, has a tandem 3 Car garage and built-in storage units.  Covered patio perfect for staying cool during the summer. A high-quality Tuff shed will satisfy all your storage needs. Inside, discover a spacious open floor plan, and ascend to the upper level, where the large den awaits you, complete with a Murphy bed and a built-in desk, this space is extremely versatile. The sizable master bedroom is a true sanctuary. Convenience is key in this home, with easy access to the freeway, shopping centers, and, conveniently positioned across from a park that offers tennis courts, running track, dog park, and walking paths. The AC units have been serviced and carpets professionally cleaned, for a move-in ready experience. This home combines elegance, functionality, and an unbeatable location.
